Package: gameday
Title: Let R tells you if your NHL team has a game today and the results for today's game
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: "Jiying Wen <wenjiying1218@gmail.com> [aut, cre]"
Description: Query live.nhle.com to check if your NHL team is listed on the
    teams that play today, and also check the scores for today's games.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.1)
Imports:
    RCurl,
    assertthat,
    jsonlite,
    stats
License: CC0
LazyData: true
Suggests:
    knitr,
    testthat,
    dplyr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
